code: @Override protected Object postProcess(Object result, Object proxy) {     if (result instanceof Connection) {         return parent.     }     if (result instanceof ResultSet) {         return Debug.proxy(new ResultSetProxy(log, result, proxy)).     }     if (result instanceof ParameterMetaData) {         return Debug.proxy(new ParameterMetaDataProxy(log, result)).     }     if (result instanceof ResultSetMetaData) {         return Debug.proxy(new ResultSetMetaDataProxy(log, result)).     }     return result. }
